{"tid":2377652,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"周六售逾新盤200伙+  CBD將軍澳佔183伙","createTime":"2021-01-23T19:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T08:20:47.000Z","uid":73269,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c04cf77c537aa40806841025e9652fa3b219dc9","tid":2377652,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2860000/2860805/SAT_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2860000%2F2860805%2FSAT_1024.jpg&h=111c2cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日出康城全新期數新盤LP10今日開售179伙，即日售出176伙，帶動整體市場氣候，特別是將軍澳新盤市場。全港新盤周六全日售逾200伙，當中將軍澳新盤佔183伙主導單日新盤成交。<br />\n<br />\n除了將軍澳LP10單日錄得成交，日出康城GRAND MARINI今日亦錄1宗成交，屬2A座63樓A室，實用面積731平方呎，屬3房大戶，成交價1294.7萬元，呎價17,711元。<br />\n<br />\n其次，將軍澳海天晉單日售出2伙現樓餘貨，包括7A座9樓D室、7A座9樓H室，成交價1,043.36萬及899.45萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2860805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2860805&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TaicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=65a4c495\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2860805</a>"},{"pid":"ec8392f7f54a4bef8fe9299e22e00bbcbce12977","tid":2377652,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"等推post"},{"pid":"d2ba7938be9c03cc9218d277ee2fb67478215bd6","tid":2377652,"uid":242102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"十問九廢答<br />\n叻極有限<br />\n拉落去睇先頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓齡逾45年， 碧瑤灣6300萬賣出， 創屋苑歷史新高<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377417</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dbc9ef73dc65d21f2087de9744d606e99137ec85","tid":2377652,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2ba7938be9c03cc9218d277ee2fb67478215bd6","tid":2377652,"uid":242102,"li